title: Remove Duplicates
description:
Write method `removeDuplicates` to remove duplicates from an unsorted linked list.

### Examples

* `1->2->3->4->3->3` -> `1->2->3->4`

### Notes

Check [LinkedListNode](https://github.com/spolnik/JAlgoArena/blob/master/src/main/java/org/algohub/engine/type/LinkedListNode.java) class. If you don't want to quit this screen, make sure you open it in a new tab.

parameters.name: node
parameters.comment: Linked List where we need to remove duplicates
